messages.content: who is the president of india

As of today, July 16, 2025, Smt. Droupadi Murmu is the 15th and current President of India [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0) [rashtrapatibhavan](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-1) [jagranjosh](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-2) [presidentofindia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-3). She took office on July 25, 2022 [presidentofindia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-3) [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-0) [rashtrapatibhavan](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-1). Notably, she is the first person from a tribal community and the second woman to hold the presidential office [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-4) [jagranjosh](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-2). Furthermore, Droupadi Murmu is the youngest individual to hold the position and the first president born in independent India [wikipedia](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-4). The President's office and residence is located in राष्ट्रपति भवन (Rashtrapati Bhavan) [rashtrapatibhavan](https://vertexaisearch.cloud.google.com/id/0-1).
